title: There is a Zeit and it Never Goes Out 2/21: Quaden Bayles, Nikki Haley, Grimes, Westworld

description:
On this edition of There is a Zeit Jack, Anna, and DJ Danl discuss the bullying of Quaden Bayles, Nikki Haley has hired Tim Chapman to her team, Grimes releases a new album, and a new Westworld trailer is out.
